{"title":"Leetcode第9题：回文数","slug":"2019090902","date":"2019-09-09T14:00:23.000Z","updated":"2019-09-09T14:09:14.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019090902.json","excerpt":"题目判断一个整数是否是回文数。回文数是指正序（从左向右）和倒序（从右向左）读都是一样的整数。","covers":["https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H8a9f04bfd82b4b53ab28953f7dafc2940.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H8c526500d5994156acff1faeaf0b4e342.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>判断一个整数是否是回文数。回文数是指正序（从左向右）和倒序（从右向左）读都是一样的整数。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h3><p>示例1：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> 121<br><strong>输出:</strong> true</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例2：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> -121<br><strong>输出:</strong> false<br><strong>解释:</strong> 从左向右读, 为 -121 。 从右向左读, 为 121- 。因此它不是一个回文数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例3：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> 10<br><strong>输出:</strong> false<br><strong>解释:</strong> 从右向左读, 为 01 。因此它不是一个回文数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"title\">isPalindrome</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String num=String.valueOf(x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(i&lt;=num.length()/<span class=\"number\">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(num.charAt(i)!=num.charAt(num.length()-<span class=\"number\">1</span>-i)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                i++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H8a9f04bfd82b4b53ab28953f7dafc2940.png\"></p>\n<p>今天上课花了不到１０分钟做的，确实很简单，原理就先不说了，大家直接看代码叭！他有有一个进阶要求是不使用字符串，改天我再试试haha。</p>\n<p>提交结果：<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/H8c526500d5994156acff1faeaf0b4e342.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/palindrome-number/\">点击去往LeetCode答题</a></p>\n","more":"<h3 id=\"示例\"><a href=\"#示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"示例\"></a>示例</h3><p>示例1：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> 121<br><strong>输出:</strong> true</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例2：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> -121<br><strong>输出:</strong> false<br><strong>解释:</strong> 从左向右读, 为 -121 。 从右向左读, 为 121- 。因此它不是一个回文数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>示例3：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入:</strong> 10<br><strong>输出:</strong> false<br><strong>解释:</strong> 从右向左读, 为 01 。因此它不是一个回文数。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> <span class=\"title\">isPalindrome</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> x)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        String num=String.valueOf(x);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(i&lt;=num.length()/<span class=\"number\">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(num.charAt(i)!=num.charAt(num.length()-<span class=\"number\">1</span>-i)) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                i++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span 